name: Love Birds iPhone Case (0141)
description:
iPhones are becoming the must have accessory. Having a personalized Cicada Case is the way for you to show off your personal style while protecting your iPhone!

✽ ABOUT THE CASE ✽

The hard plastic case has a glossy finish, and the silicone rubber case has a matte finish and wraps around the front edges of the iPhone. The designs are vibrant and professionally printed on a durable, scratch-resistant surface which results in long lasting color!

✽ HOW TO ORDER ✽

Please see our link "How To Customize Your Order" for more information about ordering a customized case.  All our images are vector images and created in house.  This means we have complete control over colors, fonts and graphics. 

Once your order is received we will send you a proof. Please be on the look out for this email, it will ensure a faster shipping time. At this time we will work with you to get the desired design.


✽ SHIPPING AND HANDLING ✽

Please allow 2 business days for production. This means, once your order has been placed and any special requests finalized... it will leave our studio within 2 business days.

We ship all orders inside the US for a flat rate of $3.50. This includes Delivery Confirmation. Your delivery confirmation number will be sent to you at the time of shipment and can be tracked at USPS.com

We DO ship international via First Class mail for a flat rate of $12.00. Please allow up to 14 days for delivery (this varies depending on location)

✽ Designed, printed and assembled at Studio Cicada in Raleigh, NC.

Wholesale pricing is available. Please email us at wholesale@studiocicada.com for info.
